burn(Pool storage,TimeswapV2PoolBurnPara.details: burn Liquidity and receive Short and Long tokenscan be only called before the maturity.after the maturity of the pool, the long0 and long1 tokens are zero. And the short tokens are added into the transaction fees.if the user wants to burn the liquidity after the maturity, they should call the collectTransactionFee function.

params.param: it is a struct that contains the parameters of the burn function.

returns.data: the data used for the callbacks.

collectProtocolFees(Pool storage,uint256.details: Collects the protocol fees of the pool.only protocol owner can call this function.if the owner enters an amount which is greater than the fee amount they have earned, withdraw only the amount they have.

params.long0Requested: The maximum amount of long0 positions wanted.
params.long1Requested: The maximum amount of long1 positions wanted.
params.shortRequested: The maximum amount of short positions wanted.

collectTransactionFees(Pool storage,uint.details: Collects the transaction fees of the pool.only liquidity provider can call this function.if the owner enters an amount which is greater than the fee amount they have earned, withdraw only the amount they have.

params.long0Requested: The maximum amount of long0 positions wanted.
params.long1Requested: The maximum amount of long1 positions wanted.
params.shortRequested: The maximum amount of short positions wanted.

deleverage(Pool storage,TimeswapV2PoolDe.details: deposit Long tokens and receive Short tokenscan be only called before the maturity.

params.param: it is a struct that contains the parameters of the deleverage function

returns.data: the data used for the callbacks.

feeGrowth(Pool storage).details: It calculates the global fee growth, which is fee increased per unit of liquidity token.

returns.long0FeeGrowth: The global fee increased per unit of liquidity token for long0.
returns.long1FeeGrowth: The global fee increased per unit of liquidity token for long1.
returns.shortFeeGrowth: The global fee increased per unit of liquidity token for short.
